  - rasterize_faces(mesh_vapor, projection, camera_params, BW, BH)
    → sorted face list (back-to-front painter's algorithm)

STEP 5 — PBR rendering into background:
  - Shadow first: add_mesh_shadow(canvas, rasterized_faces, BW, BH, scene_props, ground_y)
  - Faces: render_mesh_into_scene(canvas, rasterized, mesh_vapor, mat_ids,
                                   scene_props, camera_params, BW, BH)
    - synthesize_face_color() per face: Lambertian diffuse + Phong specular + ambient
    - Apply scene sun + ambient colors from scene_props
  - Hard edges: render_hard_edges(canvas, mesh_vapor, projection, BW, BH, scene_props)

STEP 6 — Output PNG

REPORT: mesh vertex/face count, projected vertex count, rendered faces,
        pixels written, camera parameters inferred, shadow applied
