## PART 2: SCENE-SPECIFIC MODIFIERS

Add these snippets to any template when the environment has specific characteristics.

### For Beach/Ocean Environments
```
SCENE-SPECIFIC ADDITIONS:
- Horizon line is at ~35-45% from top of image
- Water zone: below horizon in middle horizontal band (blue-dominant)
- Wet sand zone: below water, slightly darker (60-75% from top)
- Dry sand zone: bottom 25% of canvas
- Apply procedural_sand_texture() to sand zones after subject placement
- If sunset: warm_strength > 0.3, render_horizon_glow() is mandatory
